'''毛辛拉姆''' ({{IPAc-en|ˈ|m|ɔ:|s|ɪ|n|ˌ|r|ʌ|m}}) 是位於[[印度東北部|印度東北部]][[梅加拉亞邦|梅加拉亞邦]][[東卡希山縣|東卡希山縣]]的一个城鎮，距离[[西隆|西隆]]60.9公里。
毛辛拉姆是印度降雨量最大的地區，也被認為是世界上最潮濕的地區，其年平均[[降雨量|降雨量]]可達{{convert|11872|mm|in|lk=on}}<ref name="year-rain">{{cite web |url=http://wmo.asu.edu/#global |title=Global Weather & Climate Extremes |website=Arizona State University World Meteorological Organization |accessdate=2015-07-22 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208085718/http://wmo.asu.edu/#global |dead-url=no }}</ref>
<ref name="year-rain2">{{cite web | title = Meghalaya: The Wettest Place on Earth | work = The Atlantic | url = https://www.theatlantic.com/infocus/2014/08/meghalaya-the-wettest-place-on-earth/100797/ | date = 22 August 2014 | accessdate = 2014-08-23 | archive-date = 2015-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150107052004/http://www.theatlantic.com/infocus/2014/08/meghalaya-the-wettest-place-on-earth/100797 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web | title = Mawsynram, India | work = National Geographic | url = http://travel.nationalgeographic.com/travel/365-photos/rain-mawsynram-india/ | date = 4 February 2013 | accessdate = 2014-08-23 | archive-date = 2017-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171005214948/http://travel.nationalgeographic.com/travel/365-photos/rain-mawsynram-india | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。但這一稱號是有爭議的，因為在1952至1989年間，[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]][[略羅|略羅]]的年平均降雨量可達{{convert|12717|mm|in|lk=on}}<ref>http://www.banrepcultural.org/blaavirtual/faunayflora/pacific1/cap10.htm</ref><ref name="Lacerda2004">{{cite book|author=Luiz Drude de Lacerda|title=Environmental Geochemistry in Tropical and Subtropical Environments|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3th0bNos0OcC&pg=PA177|date=2004|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-3-540-42540-3|pages=177–|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803160011/https://books.google.com/books?id=3th0bNos0OcC&pg=PA177|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而同樣屬於哥倫比亞的[[洛佩斯_(考卡省)|洛佩斯]]在1960至2012年間其年平均降雨量可達{{convert|12892|mm|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wunderground.com/blog/weatherhistorian/comment.html?entrynum=135#commenttop |title=Weather Extremes : New Wettest Place on Earth Discovered? - Weather Underground |work=wunderground.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031053635/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/weatherhistorian/comment.html?entrynum=135 |archivedate=2014-10-31 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tiempo.com/ram/32180/descubierto-en-colombia-un-nuevo-lugar-mas-humedo-en-la-tierra/|title=¿Descubierto en Colombia un nuevo lugar más húmedo en la Tierra?|work=tiempo.com|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2020-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324042454/https://www.tiempo.com/ram/32180/descubierto-en-colombia-un-nuevo-lugar-mas-humedo-en-la-tierra/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據《[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]》，1985年毛辛拉姆的年降雨量達到了{{convert|26000|mm|in}}。

==位置==
毛辛拉姆位於[[乞拉朋吉|乞拉朋吉]]以西15千米處，海拔約1400米。

