根據柯本氣候分類法，毛辛拉姆屬於亞熱帶高原氣候(Cwb)。當地雨量充沛，多為陣雨，季風期長而旱季短。根據近幾十年的數據，它或許是世界上最潮濕的地方，或者說是年平均降雨量最高的地方<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kuttippurath|first=J|last2=Murasingh|first2=S|last3=Stott|first3=P A|last4=Sarojini|first4=B Balan|last5=Jha|first5=Madan K|last6=Kumar|first6=P|last7=Nair|first7=P J|last8=Varikoden|first8=H|last9=Raj|first9=S|last10=Francis|first10=P A|last11=Pandey|first11=P C|date=2021-01-22|title=Observed rainfall changes in the past century (1901–2019) over the wettest place on Earth|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1748-9326/abcf78|journal=Environmental Research Letters|volume=16|issue=2|pages=024018|doi=10.1088/1748-9326/abcf78|issn=1748-9326|doi-access=free|access-date=2021-04-02|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129141705/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1748-9326/abcf78|dead-url=no}}</ref>。毛辛拉姆的年平均降雨量超過10000毫米，且絕大部分降雨都發生在[[季風|季風]]月份<ref>''The Tribune'', Chandigarh, August 2003. {{full citation needed}}</ref>。

